person

Class CollegeEmployee

  • java.lang.Object
    • person.Person
      • person.CollegeEmployee

  • public class CollegeEmployee
extends Person
    CollegeEmployee is a class that extends super class Person which allows user to type in data for college employee. This class makes use of JOptionPane class to accept GUI inputs.

    1.0
    Author:
    Philip Bryan Datoon
